'''Alliance Search & Rescue Teams''' were groups of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] operatives dedicated to locating and liberating prisoners of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. The teams were responsible for the discovery of prisoners from [[Echo Base/Legends|Echo Base]] such as [[Kupalo]] and their subsequent rescue from ''[[VTR-LX]]'', where they were being held.

